{
  "id": "adv_card_skr_52_03",
  "title": "川咲さくら 3話 がぶー！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さん\n{user}さん！　大丈夫ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…{user}-san\n{user}-san! Are you alright?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "はっ……！？　さ、さくらか……\nここは一体……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh…!? S-Sakura…\nWhere are we…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、寝ぼけてるんですか？\nここはラーメン屋さんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ are you sleep-talking?\nThis is a ramen shop",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.5319275539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.1985942205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ら、ラーメン……！？\n俺達はレストランにいたはずじゃ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Ramen…!?\nWeren't we at a restaurant…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "違いますよ～シメのシメに味噌ラーメンを\n食べようって言って出て来たじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ that's not it~ We came here because I suggested having\nmiso ramen as the last finished off",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.866236051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 29.3329027177
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "ほら{user}さん、早く食べないと\n味噌ラーメンが伸びちゃいますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on {user}-san‚ don't eat quickly‚\nthe miso ramen will get soggy?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.266236051,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったか……言われてみればそんな気もするな\nただ、もうお腹が一杯で入らないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Was that the case… Now that you mention it‚ I guess that's true\nBut‚ I'm already full and can't eat any more",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.0705443384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃ、じゃあ……その味噌ラーメン\n私がもらってもいいですか？　ごくり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ then… that miso ramen\ncan I have some? Gulp…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6038776717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "俺は構わないが……そんなに食べて大丈夫か？\nそれにさくら、なんだか目が怖いぞ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't mind‚ but… you'll be right eating that much?\nAnd Sakura‚ your eyes look kind of scary…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.9081859591
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr006.m4a",
      "text": "平気です！　この気持ち、もう抑えられません……！\n私、青春全部かけて味噌ラーメンを食べますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm fine! I can't hold back these feelings‚ anymore…!\nI'll put all my youth into eating this miso ramen!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9415192924,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_ramen-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7233.333333399997,
          "startTime": 74.1748526258
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.5081859591
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr007.m4a",
      "text": "いただきまーす！　ん～！\nとろとろのチャーシューが口の中でとろけます～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's eatー! Mmm~!\nThe tender char siu melts in my mouth~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.0415192924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr008.m4a",
      "text": "それに、味噌とバターの甘じょっぱいスープ\nまるでジュースみたいに飲めちゃいます！　ごくごく",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And the sweet miso and butter soup\nIt's so good I could drink it like juice! Gulp‚ gulp!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7415192924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.6748526258
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr009.m4a",
      "text": "はわぁ～美味し過ぎていくらでもいけちゃいそうだよ～\n北海道……グルメで正気を保っているのが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa~‚ it's so good‚ I could eat it forever~\nHokkaido… it's amazing how much food keeps people sane…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.1748526258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "お、おいさくら、そんなに食べて本当に大丈夫なのか？\nお腹を壊したりしたら大変だぞ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Hey‚ Sakura‚ are you sure you're okay eating that much?\nIt'll be terrible if you get a stomachache…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.0427893005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr010.m4a",
      "text": "分かってます！　分かってるんですけど……\nラーメンが美味し過ぎて手が止まらないんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know! I know‚ but…\nThe ramen is delicious‚ so I can't stop!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.4761226339,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 121.7761302633
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr011.m4a",
      "text": "あの、もう一杯、もう一杯だけ食べていいですか！？\nそうじゃないと私、おかしくなってしまいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ just one more‚ can I have just one more bowl!?\nOtherwise‚ I'll go insane!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.2427969299,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10523.869736799981,
          "startTime": 138.7666666667
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11657.203070099997,
          "startTime": 139.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 133.3427969299
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "さくら、一旦落ち着くんだ！　ほら、箸を置いて！\nくっ、凄い力で箸を持っていてびくともしないぞ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ calm down! Here‚ put your chopsticks down!\nDamn‚ she's holding the chopsticks with incredible strength‚ they won't budge…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6679952145,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rope-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3325.198284599992,
          "startTime": 136.6679952145
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr012.m4a",
      "text": "……無理です。お腹が空いてたまらないんです！\nうう……次のラーメンを待てそうにありません……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…can't help. I’m so hungry I can’t stand it!\nUgh… I can't wait for the next ramen…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.5173770271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.5173770271
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr013.m4a",
      "text": "それより……{user}さんの腕、じゅるり\nほどよく肉が付いていてチャーシューみたいですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More than that… {user}-san's arm‚ gulp\nIt's got the right amount of meat on it‚ looks like char siu…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.0173770271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "お、おいさくら、変な目で俺を見るんじゃない\n凄く怖いんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Hey Sakura‚ don't look at me like that…\nIt's really scary…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 171.9493117018
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-skr014.m4a",
      "text": "うう、もう我慢出来ません……ちょっとだけ……\n一口だけでいいから味見させて下さい！　がぶー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh‚ I can't stand anymore… just…\nJust one bite‚ please let me taste it! Chompー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.5605121239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_ramen-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "ramen-00-noon",
      "startTime": 184.9493040724
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ぎゃぁぁ！　さくら、俺を食べないでくれー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aaaah! Sakura‚ don't eat meー!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.8159844719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 193.96362594
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_famires-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "famires-00-night",
      "startTime": 193.96362594
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03/sud_vo_adv_card_skr_52_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　こ、ここは……！？\n俺は今まで何を……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh! W-Where am I…!?\nWhat have I been doing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.1666737874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
